author: Al Jazeera
title: Thousands of Indonesians journey home, despite virus warnings
description: Nearly 90 percent of Indonesians are Muslim and usually return to their home villages at the end of Ramadan to celebrate Eid with their families.
content:
Indonesian authorities are urging millions of citizens not to travel back to their hometowns to celebrate next month's Muslim festival of Eid.
